SUMMARY:Wilderness Union Adventure Trivia
DESCRIPTION:Wilderness Union Toronto - Outdoor Adventure and Hiking Club\n
 **This event is open to all - you'll just need to register for this event 
 [our website](https://www.wildernessunion.com/landing/adventure-trivia) to
  confirm your place.**\n\nWe've teamed up with the legendary Quizmaster Je
 ss team and MEC to bring you a night dedicated entirely to the backcountry
 . Expect a room full of people who would rather be in a tent than a cubicl
 e\, battling it out over survival stories\, epic expeditions\, and gear kn
 owledge.\n\n**Why You Should Be There:**\n**\\- The Prize\\.** We've got 3
  prize packs of **premium outdoor gear worth over $400** to give away cour
 tesy of MEC.\n**\\- The Community\\.** You'll get to meet a crew who have 
 big plans to explore this summer.\n**\\- The Hosting\\.** Analisa from the
  Quizmaster Jess team is at the helm\, bringing seven years of expertise t
 o ensure the night is filled with banter\, curveballs\, and great energy.\
 n\n**What to Expect**\n**High-Stakes Competition.** Multiple rounds of nat
 ure-adjacent trivia spanning roughly two hours of gameplay.\n**Solo-Friend
 ly Setup.** We specialize in matching solo adventurers with friendly teams
  because the best stories usually start with meeting a stranger.\n‍**Gre
 at Food and Drinks.** Saint John’s Tavern offers a full pub menu and a w
 ide selection of drinks available at your table throughout the entire even
 ing.\n\n**Highlights**\nMEC Prizes. Quizmaster Jess Team. Meet the Crew.\n
 \n**Event cost: from $9 + HST**\n**Register [here.](https://www.wilderness
 union.com/landing/adventure-trivia)**\n\n**About Wilderness Union**\nWilde
 rness Union is deliberate about building an outdoors community that connec
 ts you to the life-changing magic of the outdoors and helps you find your 
 people.\n\nMembers range from 20-40 years old. The group is a mix of GTA l
 ocals and newcomers to Toronto from within Canada and abroad.\n\nAttendanc
 e numbers on Meetup don't reflect our actual event attendance - we typical
 ly have 15-20 community members at each event. Large enough that there's s
 omeone new to meet but small enough that it's not overwhelming!\n\n***Lear
 n more at our website [www.wildernessunion.com](https://www.wildernessunio
 n.com/)***
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wildernessunion/events/313793082/
